staging: comedi: hwdrv_apci1564: use addi_tcw.h defines

Use the ADDI_TCW_CTRL_REG bit defines in addi_tcw.h to remove the "magic"
numbers.

Add some missing bit defines and mask defines to addi_tcw.h to help
cleanup the code.

